		<div class="post-super-wrapper" role="main" data-id="3888423" data-primary-cat="" data-permalink="https://newsone.com/3888423/nyc-subway-fare-evasion-guerrilla-campaign/" data-title="‘Don&#8217;t Snitch. Swipe’ Guerrilla Subway Fare Evasion Fliers Call Out NYC’s Latest &#8216;Broken Windows&#8217; Policing">

			<div class="in-content-widget-top">
